# Integrations

## Supabase

- Auth, Postgres, Storage, RLS — primary backend
- Clients in `lib/supabase/`; never duplicate client factories

## OpenAI (Vercel AI SDK)

- `lib/ai/` — prompt templates, outline generation, slide content fill
- Model config via env; log usage to `ai_generations` table

## Inngest

- `lib/inngest/` — client, event definitions, function handlers
- Events: `deck/generate`, `deck/export`, `email/send`
- Verify signing key on webhook route

## Stripe

- `lib/stripe/` — checkout, portal, webhook handler
- Map Stripe customer to org; sync subscription status to DB

## Resend

- Transactional email: welcome, export ready, invite
- Templates in `lib/email/`; no marketing blasts from app code

## Sentry

- `@sentry/nextjs` — error tracking, performance traces
- Tag events with `org_id` (non-PII) for debugging

## PostHog

- Client-side analytics in dashboard only
- Track: deck created, outline approved, export completed

## Rules

- Wrap each provider in a thin lib module with typed interfaces
- Graceful degradation when optional integrations are unconfigured (dev)
- All webhooks: verify signature, return 200 quickly, process async
